CIDR range this means servers will get created inside vpc, vpc will be created after that divide small parts as called subnets servers will get
created inside this subnets for every server will have a public IP & private Ip Public Ip will provide from AWS and private IP will come from VPC 



what is meat by subnet is by dividing a large network into a small small networks called as subnets.

